{"tid":2045783,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"支那根本就係丁蟹所以單靠美國係贏唔到支那","createTime":"2020-06-01T04:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T05:20:43.000Z","uid":275238,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"16ec9c7a20447de4ab29f20847a399bd6ee2f798","tid":2045783,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:19:59.000Z","msg":"大時代真係神劇，幾十年前已預示咗今天嘅世界格局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n丁蟹蠻不講理之餘仲要覺得自己好有道理十足十依家嘅支那，錯手打死幫過佢嘅老友(香港)，但又成世行運連老狐狸陳萬賢(英國)都唔夠佢鬥，之後陳滔滔(美國)用高科技都要輸俾丁蟹，最後搞到要『借運』先贏到丁蟹<br />\n<br />\n依家抗爭已經去到陳滔滔依個階段，所以我預示美國都會輸(其實已經輸緊俾武漢肺炎)，所以我相信點樣『借運』將會係決勝關鍵但究竟點樣先可以做到『借運』依招絕殺就暫時都仲未參透到。。。"},{"pid":"10fbaaf04cea9e6317cc4e4ba51dacc2bbec2728","tid":2045783,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:21:01.000Z","msg":"英國對支那講: 咁多人死, 唔見你死?"},{"pid":"edaf28e6e323c94d987cf49e46b7f0f9c9719a88","tid":2045783,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:21:25.000Z","msg":"咁邊個係方展博? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462728a7216a6b81f396831a9215e4f3c036ac33","tid":2045783,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"edaf28e6e323c94d987cf49e46b7f0f9c9719a88","tid":2045783,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:21:25.000Z","msg":"咁邊個係方展博? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:23:28.000Z","msg":"諗下邊個最憎大陸，似台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826e3b24dcfc4faf0ae45f81472d80fa88254381","tid":2045783,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"462728a7216a6